epic.network

Class NetworkOfIndividualsModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • epic.sir.IndividualBasedModel
      • epic.network.NetworkOfIndividualsModel

  • public class NetworkOfIndividualsModel
extends IndividualBasedModel
    NetworkOfIndividualsModel contains individuals (individual network agents) in a network, and infection (SIR) or exposure (SEIR) may only occur between connected individuals. Otherwise the behaviour is the same as IndividualBasedModel (a stochastic SIR/SEI in epic.sir).
    Version:
    9 June 2014
    Author:
    Samantha Lycett
